This directory is an attempt to do bayesian directed segmentation.

Here is a walkthrough of usage:

1) Start Matlab
2) Change Matlab directory to this directory.
3) >> SegmentImages('~/Desktop/2011-06-13_000/Well E04', 'DsRed - Confocal - n', '.tif', 6, 854, 858, 'output')
4) Correct
5) Hit "Save"
6) Close
7) Yes to add to training set.
8) Repeat, lather, rinse
9) Next is the "validation set", begins with Naive segment.
10) Close